org.apache.commons.rdf.jena

Interface JenaQuadLike<G extends RDFTerm>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JenaTripleLike, QuadLike<G>, TripleLike
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JenaGeneralizedQuadLike, JenaQuad

    public interface JenaQuadLike<G extends RDFTerm>
extends JenaTripleLike, QuadLike<G>
    A QuadLike wrapper of a Jena Quad.

    This is a marker interface common to its specializations JenaQuad and JenaGeneralizedQuadLike.

    See Also:
    JenaQuad, JenaGeneralizedQuadLike
